Проверка гипотез¶

Гипотиза 1¶

: c Xbox One PC ;

H_0: c    Xbox One  PC 
H_1: c    Xbox One  PC  
alpha = 0.05
In [83]:
# results =     
# alpha -   


xone = data.query('platform == "XOne" and ~user_score.isna()')['user_score']
pc = data.query('platform == "PC" and ~user_score.isna()')['user_score']

results = st.ttest_ind(xone, pc, equal_var = False)

alpha = 0.05
#   p-value   
print(results.pvalue)
#       
if results.pvalue < alpha:
    print('  ')
else:
    print('    ')
    

0.11601398086668832

, Xbox One PC

Гипотеза 2¶

: Action Sports ;

H_0:     Action  Sports  
H_1:     Action  Sports 
alpha = 0.05
In [84]:
# results =     
# alpha -   

action = data.query('genre == "Action" and ~user_score.isna()')['user_score']
sports = data.query('genre == "Sports" and ~user_score.isna()')['user_score']

results = st.ttest_ind(action, sports, equal_var = False)

alpha = 0.05
#   p-value   
print(results.pvalue)
#       
if results.pvalue < alpha:
    print('    ')    
else:
    print('  ')

1.1825550382644557e-14

, Action Sports
